# Imports the SAME common.fnk but via a deliberately different raw
# relative path (`../sub/common.fnk`) to exercise canonical-URL dedup:
# both left.fnk and right.fnk must share a single linked copy of
# common.fnk despite reaching it through different strings.
# Canonical form (entry-relative): ./sub/common.fnk
{base} = import '../sub/common.fnk'

right_val = base + 2
